autorotate (0.4) karmic; urgency=low

  * Added .conf file to allow creation of system bus
  * manual-rotate.py notifies the user when automatic rotation is
    enabled/disabled via libnotify 
  * Added dbus .service file describing the autorotate service
  * Fixed the dependencies in the debian control file 
  * Check if autorotate daemon already running before starting another
    one

